{"tid":2298942,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"第一日做鴨","createTime":"2020-11-24T11:41:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T16:04:28.000Z","uid":234509,"like":20,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"00bf4ae079c67a02bb12368b2b25f4a4231039ca","tid":2298942,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:41:13.000Z","msg":"之前從來做過鴨，第一轉就要俾人摸8次，頂硬上，係就係怕醜咗少少，去完一轉，條野已經好硬，第二轉俾人摸8次已經J軟，行唔到咁，個客睇量我，摸住6次先，勉強頂到，好不容易先捱到中午飯，去左沙田一間茶餐廳到食，咁送左例湯黎， 攞起隻匙羹，我屌，提唔能起，右手已經硬能曬，我要用個頭壓低黎飲湯，心諗，仆街喇，重有半日點捱，好，食完飯，又做過，又攰又忙，我知再唔飲水，一定會死，我愉雞經過7-11買支野飲，一野飲曬都唔夠，但起碼有返精神，到放工時，佢地問我返唔返第二日，我話唔返，第日就辭職，好敬佩佢地，份工真係唔簡單"},{"pid":"bf422fa03e2784ca9149724f71f11f6dcbfb48ac","tid":2298942,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:41:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ccb75b6c0ec86ba5def13670a3b68ce51dfa8d","tid":2298942,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c769c0fc65e0c85916f5c1e0db3ea9d9f47dc20a","tid":2298942,"uid":255350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:42:16.000Z","msg":"帥兄一日幾多錢"},{"pid":"9063e079dfcb10244371466c96316890d166c296","tid":2298942,"uid":255350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:42:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>師兄一日幾多錢</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e681b859e363df0bf9eabf9ae6713ba812c48b20","tid":2298942,"uid":234509,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c769c0fc65e0c85916f5c1e0db3ea9d9f47dc20a","tid":2298942,"uid":255350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:42:16.000Z","msg":"帥兄一日幾多錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:43:22.000Z","msg":"Ot嘅話有1m"},{"pid":"05aaec482763a9410a8c3fcadc743e89529b2cab","tid":2298942,"uid":25204,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedB